---
title: Middle Eastern Chicken & Pumpkin Salad with Chickpeas, Pickled Onion & Lemon Yoghurt Dressing
description: Tender pan-fried chicken breast is the perfect match for our ras el hanout spice mix shine, and when you add roasted pumpkin, crunchy chickpeas and crisp greens, you get a bowl of pure goodness. Enjoy!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/middle-eastern-chicken-pumpkin-salad-f9550357.jpg
